{"tid":261664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"左上右落是常識吧","createTime":"2017-05-28T15:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T14:00:38.000Z","uid":75115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2eeb7fb4ad06d8ff68437c22348a5b0c286d28d6","tid":261664,"uid":75115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T15:37:44.000Z","msg":"上落樓梯有左上右落喱個觀念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特別係多人o既時候更加要遵守<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左放係樓梯到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得係馬路到都應該要實行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n趕時間o既時候過馬路，要左閃右避先過到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲會無啦啦同人面對面，搞到要急殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時o的馬路又多又長， 趕時間真係行到躁底<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf8ea2e2eae4961c25105bf420e3e8d1b0880cd","tid":261664,"uid":88495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T15:52:55.000Z","msg":"我覺得左上右落都係錯既因為佢應用係上同落既話會撞<br />\n所以係要右上右落or左上左落<br />\n有冇人明我講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"217f83c6755479ac9b3c640e540242f19fba4df5","tid":261664,"uid":21521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T15:54:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得左上右落都係錯既因為佢應用係上同落既話會撞<br />\n所以係要右上右落or左上左落<br />\n有冇人明我講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明白，應該總係靠右行或總係靠左行"},{"pid":"775119de63028cb59a9c6f4efe2ec150b3137420","tid":261664,"uid":100242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T15:56:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得左上右落都係錯既因為佢應用係上同落既話會撞<br />\n所以係要右上右落or左上左落<br />\n有冇人明我講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明你講咩不過唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上係指你行嘅方向，落就相反，所以左上右落係啱嘅咁樣每